{
  "texts": [
    "Surely what we outside critics should be doing, is not sitting back being ready to be impressed by the latest technology but applying our specialist skills to act as a 'red team' facing up to AI's 'blue team'.",
    "For that purpose, it is useful to argue that the blue team will 'never' manage this or that without doing 'this or that'.",
    "When/if we are proved wrong, we will all have learned something.",
